      "startTime": 0.3333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、ちょうど良かった\n今から、葵を探しに行こうとしてたところだったんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ just in time.\nI was about to go look for Aoi.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.266666611,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "rouka",
      "startTime": 6.6278459867
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01-aoi001.m4a",
      "text": "……何かあったの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Did something happen?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.6278459867,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "葵に仕事の話がきてな\n今までと毛色が違うから、まずは相談しないとと思って",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There's a job offer for you‚ Aoi.\nIt's a bit different from what you've done before‚ so I thought I'd discuss it with you first.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.7000008345,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "rouka",
      "startTime": 16.1967131854
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01-aoi002.m4a",
      "text": "君は僕達のマネージャーなんだから\nいちいち僕に相談しないで、OKしても良かったのに",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You're our manager.\nYou could have just accepted it without consulting me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.7633798521,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "rouka",
      "startTime": 22.230046646
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01-aoi003.m4a",
      "text": "それで、一体{user}君が\n悩むほどの仕事ってなんなの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ what kind of job is it that\nhas {user} so concerned?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.3967133126,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "ほら、前にすずがドラマにゲスト出演しただろう？\n毎週、殺人事件を解決していく……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Remember when Suzu guest-starred on that drama?\nThe one where they solve a murder case every week…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.5333332778,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "rouka",
      "startTime": 34.4880729836
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01-aoi004.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、あれ。僕も観たよ\n今度は僕に、あのドラマへの出演依頼がきたの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ that one. I watched it too.\nSo‚ now they're asking me to star on that drama?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.2214063169,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "rouka",
      "startTime": 42.3547381243
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01-aoi005.m4a",
      "text": "それで、僕は一体何をすればいいんだい\n死体役？　スキップしながら包丁振り回すとか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What am I supposed to do?\nPlay a corpse? Or running around waving a knife?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.7547381243,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "……結構やる気だな\nダンス以外の仕事は嫌がるかと思ってたんだが",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…You seem pretty eager.\nI thought you'd dislike work outside of dancing.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.1999968927,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "rouka",
      "startTime": 55.9294088126
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01-aoi006.m4a",
      "text": "リズノワの躍進のためにはなんでもやると言ったからね\n演技は未経験だけど、頑張ってみるよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I said I'd do anything for LizNoir's success.\nI have no acting experience‚ but I'll give it my best shot.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.0627421459,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}